Global HER2-Positive Breast Cancer Market Insights
HER2-Positive Breast Cancer Market size was valued at USD 25.4 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 38.6 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 6.8% from 2024 to 2030.

HER2-Positive Breast Cancer Market Overview
The HER2-Positive Breast Cancer Market is projected to reach a value of $24.5 billion by 2028, with a strong CAGR of 11.3% from 2023 to 2028. This growth is driven by advancements in targeted therapies, an increasing prevalence of breast cancer, and the rise of personalized medicine. The market has seen significant investments in research and development, leading to the development of innovative HER2-targeted therapies. Additionally, ongoing clinical trials and growing awareness about breast cancer treatment options are expected to drive the demand for HER2-positive breast cancer therapeutics.

